ed 25 x 25 cell grid of letters with a =C2=A3350,000 estimate and a third-p=
arty guarantee. The guarantee isn=E2=80=99t surprising considering one of t=
hese 1988 25 x 25 works, also from the same collection but composed of a se=
ries of 25 smaller 5 x 5 cell panels, sold for nearly $900,000 in March. <b=
r/></td>
